```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Multiply["alma_multiply_full"]
        M1[Validate inputs] --> M2{n <= 256?}
        M2 -->|Yes| M3[Single dgemm]
        M2 -->|No| M4[Allocate metadata]
        M4 --> M5[Parallel block multiply<br/>OpenMP collapse(2)]
        M5 --> M6[For each (bi,bj) output]
        M6 --> M7[For each bk summation]
        M7 --> M8[dgemm accumulation<br/>alpha=0 first, then 1]
        M8 --> M9[Free metadata]
        M9 --> M10[Return]
    end
```

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class BlockMeta {
        +BlockType type
        +int rows
        +int cols
        +int rank
        +int ld
        +double* U
        +double* S
        +double* VT
    }

    class MatrixBlock {
        +double* data
        +BlockMeta meta
    }

    class TunedConfig {
        +int blockSize
        +bool useOpenBLAS
        +bool initialized
    }

    MatrixBlock --> BlockMeta
```

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant alma_multiply
    participant alma_multiply_full
    participant compute_block_meta
    participant LAPACK
    participant multiply_lowrank_block
    participant BLAS

    User->>alma_multiply: alma_multiply(A, B, C, n, blockSize)
    alma_multiply->>alma_multiply_full: alma_multiply_full(A, B, C, n, blockSize)
    
    alma_multiply_full->>alma_multiply_full: Validate params
    alma_multiply_full->>alma_multiply_full: n <= 256?
    
    alt Small matrix
        alma_multiply_full->>BLAS: cblas_dgemm(A, B, C)
    else Blocked multiply
        alma_multiply_full->>compute_block_meta: For each block in A
        compute_block_meta->>LAPACK: LAPACKE_dgesvd
        LAPACK-->>compute_block_meta: U, S, VT
        compute_block_meta-->>alma_multiply_full: BlockMeta
        
        alma_multiply_full->>compute_block_meta: For each block in B
        compute_block_meta->>LAPACK: LAPACKE_dgesvd
        LAPACK-->>compute_block_meta: U, S, VT
        
        alma_multiply_full->>alma_multiply_full: Parallel for (bi, bj)
        loop For each bk
            alt Both LowRank
                alma_multiply_full->>multiply_lowrank_block: U_a*S_a*V_a^T × U_b*S_b*V_b^T
                multiply_lowrank_block-->>alma_multiply_full: C_block
            else Any Dense
                alma_multiply_full->>BLAS: cblas_dgemm(block)
                BLAS-->>alma_multiply_full: C_block
            end
        end
    end
    
    alma_multiply_full-->>User: AlmaError::Success
```

